詳細資訊會比較好，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想你應該已經知道了，<delay20 />
10月31日是萬聖節喔。<10_4 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好糖果了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我現在<delay8 />比起糖果，
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反而更煩惱要裝扮成什麼樣子。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />傷腦筋，<delay8 />到底該怎麼打扮才好<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節終於要到了。<delay frames="40" />
